      "content": "i mean i appreciate the help but it feels so hollow. like, the numbers on a phone won't change the fact that i have zero footprint here. if i just... drifted away, if i just wasn't part of this world anymore, it feels more like a quiet release than a tragedy. like everything would just settle back into place without me.",
